==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pay Cerps
<hw>Pay Cerps</hw>. <def>A staff corps in the United States navy,
consisting of pay directors, pay inspectors, paymasters, passed
assistant paymasters, and assistant paymasters, having relative rank
from captain to ensign, respectively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pay rock</ent>⟦br⟧
<ent>Pay dirt</ent>⟦br⟧
